_sText:
This is the third oasis map in the series.
The season for this map is autumn and the oasis water has got higher.
This time you are armed with a m4a1 , usp , grenades and knife.
It is also raining in the map.
this map can take up to a maximum of 40 players.
I am also making an ak47 version , but if you have any more ideas on weapons you would like to see or different themes please tell me via pm or comment on my profile or even here , thankyou.
